OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA warm sunny
OL,6,Fevening then dry with clear periods
OL,7,Fovernight. Some low cloud developing
OL,8,Fover Dumfries and Galloway in the
OL,9,Fevening, spreading further east
OL,10,Fovernight. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FSomewhat cloudy to start,
OL,13,Fespecially the Southwest, this burning
OL,14,Foff in the morning. Then dry with some
OL,15,Fgood sunny spells, turning hazier in
OL,16,Fthe afternoon. Becoming very warm to
OL,17,Fhot.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
