OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry on
OL,6,FFriday with plenty of sunshine,
OL,7,Fbecoming very warm or hot. Cooler and
OL,8,Fcloudier in the east at the weekend
OL,9,Fwith some haar, brighter and warmer
OL,10,Fwest.
